name: 威尔·布兰斯克
name_full: 威尔·布兰斯克 Will Branske
introduction: Will Branske  has been in a number of national commercials, created and produced his own web series that he also stars in ("Accessory to Friendship"), and has performed in a handful of short films since moving to Los Angeles.He moved to LA from a small town in the Bay Area called Clayton.  He played sports all of his childhood and early adulthood but eventually found his passion was on the stage.  After performing in show choir, musicals, and theater he was hooked on acting and soon decided to move down to LA to see what adventures he could get himself into in this industry.In addition to acting and writing he loves to get out of town and give in to his Instagram addiction in the mountains, the desert, the beach, the forest, and, well, you get the idea.
